290
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:33,280
Why don't we just arrest them?

291
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,080
Let me say it again.

292
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:39,160
To catch drug dealers,
you must catch them red-handed.

293
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,760
Otherwise, you can't charge them
with drug trafficking.

294
00:15:42,040 --> 00:15:44,440
