307
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,040
You're a grown man.

308
00:16:07,040 --> 00:16:08,600
What's there to be afraid of
when taking a few photos?

309
00:16:10,680 --> 00:16:11,080
Alright.

310
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:12,280
I'll go investigate Erjin's situation.

311
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:13,320
Yao, you go to the hospital

312
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,400
