take care of Xiaoguang.

315
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,480
How about I investigate Erjin instead?

316
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:24,920
I've noticed you're all
getting more and more picky,

317
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,640
