318
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:28,240
Fine. You investigate Erjin.

319
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:29,240
I'll go to the hospital.

320
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:29,520
Alright.

321
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:30,520
I'll head to the hospital.

322
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,480
Be careful, Uncle.

323
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:34,480
