389
00:20:26,340 --> 00:20:27,660
You're not a neighbor.

390
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:28,780
You're just a buddy.

391
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:29,740
Alright.

392
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:30,420
Enough.

393
00:20:30,580 --> 00:20:31,260
What are you up to?

394
00:20:31,300 --> 00:20:32,100
Alright,

395
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:33,020
Zheng Nan,

396
00:20:33,260 --> 00:20:35,300
you never take things seriously.

397
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:42,540
If you're tired, grab a few bites,

398
00:20:42,620 --> 00:20:43,700
and then we'll head back.

399
00:20:44,660 --> 00:20:46,260
How can you not be tired
after working all night?

400
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:48,580
Eat quickly so you can leave.

401
00:20:48,740 --> 00:20:49,700
I'll keep watch here.

402
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:52,100
Uncle, you should leave
once you're done eating too.

403
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:54,940
If I leave, who will take care of you?

404
00:20:54,940 --> 00:20:56,500
Isn't she here?

405
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:58,100
She used to chase me around
and beat me up when I was a kid.

406
00:20:58,100 --> 00:20:59,060
Now I finally get a chance

407
00:20:59,060 --> 00:21:00,660
to make her take care of me.

408
00:21:00,700 --> 00:21:02,380
She's so lazy.

409
00:21:03,740 --> 00:21:05,820
I need to give her a chance
to correct her ways

410
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:07,420
and be productive.

411
00:21:14,060 --> 00:21:14,860
Nan.

412
00:21:15,620 --> 00:21:16,780
You started eating by yourself?

413
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:18,340
You're supposed to be
taking care of the patient.

414
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:19,660
You're just eating by yourself?

415
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:21,020
Give him something to eat.

416
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:23,420
Meat.

417
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:25,180
Did I forget about you? Here.

418
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:27,140
What are you doing?

419
00:21:27,140 --> 00:21:28,180
You might as well stab him to death.

420
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:29,580
You've almost got the chopsticks
at the back of his head.

421
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:34,100
Sorry.

422
00:21:34,100 --> 00:21:34,860
My bad.

423
00:21:37,180 --> 00:21:38,300
Eat quickly and get out of here.

424
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:39,740
The nurse has quite a temper.

425
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:45,340
Xiaoguang,

426
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:48,860
if you like
being taken care of like this,

427
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:50,340
I'll leave her here.

428
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:51,740
You take good care of him.

429
00:21:52,060 --> 00:21:53,100
I'll take Uncle away.

430
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:55,420
If you insist, I guess I could manage.

431
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:57,900
Give me a bite of that dish.

432
00:21:59,940 --> 00:22:00,740
That dish.

433
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:13,560
[Halan's Old Brand:
State-owned Cold Noodle Restaurant]

434
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:20,060
Do you need me to open it for you?

435
00:22:20,380 --> 00:22:21,020
Yes.

436
00:22:22,340 --> 00:22:23,820
Your cold noodles are really good.

437
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:24,660
Of course,

438
00:22:24,660 --> 00:22:25,900
we're an old brand.

439
00:22:25,900 --> 00:22:26,940
We have a lot of regular customers.

440
00:22:26,940 --> 00:22:27,620
Really?

441
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:29,860
A friend recommended this place to me.

442
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:31,300
Not sure if you remember him.

443
00:22:31,780 --> 00:22:33,100
He's from the south,

444
00:22:33,380 --> 00:22:34,540
has asthma,

445
00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:36,820
and often carries an inhaler.

446
00:22:38,740 --> 00:22:39,500
I remember.

447
00:22:39,700 --> 00:22:41,020
Is he a short guy

448
00:22:41,020 --> 00:22:42,100
with dark skin?

449
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:43,020
Yes.

450
00:22:43,020 --> 00:22:44,420
He's one of our regular customers too.

451
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:45,900
He came by for noodles
every now and then.

452
00:22:46,820 --> 00:22:47,580
Thank you.

453
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:48,940
No problem.
Call me if you need anything.

454
00:22:49,020 --> 00:22:49,660
Alright.

455
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:06,220
Time to work.

456
00:23:09,500 --> 00:23:10,340
What's the matter?

457
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:12,180
