465
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:39,500
Want to go together today?

466
00:23:40,980 --> 00:23:41,980
I don't feel like running.

467
00:23:42,540 --> 00:23:43,380
Have some exercise.

468
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:45,420
Let's go.

469
00:24:09,260 --> 00:24:10,060
Mom,

470
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:11,220
