485
00:24:49,340 --> 00:24:50,340
Exactly the same.

486
00:24:50,820 --> 00:24:51,620
That's great.

487
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:52,460
Yao.

488
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:53,780
Get Director Gao for me.

489
00:24:53,860 --> 00:24:54,340
Got it.

490
00:24:54,580 --> 00:24:55,140
On it.

491
00:24:55,580 --> 00:24:56,380
By the way,

492
00:24:57,260 --> 00:24:58,460
