493
00:24:58,940 --> 00:25:00,060
Xiaoguang's fine.

494
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:01,020
Just some scrapes.

495
00:25:02,980 --> 00:25:03,780
Keep going.

496
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:05,780
We have a major discovery this time.

497
00:25:06,140 --> 00:25:07,700
The meth from the White Building

498
00:25:07,820 --> 00:25:09,180
