501
00:25:14,140 --> 00:25:16,220
This proves that this meth

502
00:25:16,340 --> 00:25:18,420
isn't just appearing in Halan randomly.

503
00:25:18,580 --> 00:25:20,060
It's being sold in an organized manner.

504
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:21,500
Additionally, we've identified

505
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:22,300
the name of this meth.

506
00:25:22,300 --> 00:25:23,380
It's called Lucifer.

507
00:25:24,020 --> 00:25:25,740
The person controlling Lucifer

508
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:27,900
is known only by a codename,

509
00:25:28,020 --> 00:25:29,420
"Mr. Ma."

510
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:31,220
Is Mr. Ma this Qin Yi?

511
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:33,100
We can't confirm that yet.

512
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:34,100
Where's the warehouse?

513
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:36,740
We've had people monitoring
the Sanlianer Factory,

514
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:38,580
but so far,

515
00:25:38,580 --> 00:25:40,980
