00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:05,420
Uncle!

522
00:26:05,780 --> 00:26:06,900
Why are you back?

523
00:26:06,980 --> 00:26:08,340
I'm almost recovered.

524
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:09,340
What did the doctor...

525
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:11,180
Director Gao?

526
00:26:12,420 --> 00:26:13,220
