Understood.

569
00:27:24,900 --> 00:27:25,540
- Yes.
- Yes.

570
00:27:28,380 --> 00:27:29,500
- Director Gao, see you.
- Take care.

571
00:27:29,940 --> 00:27:30,940
Thank you, Director Gao,
for your concern.

572
00:27:36,940 --> 00:27:37,780
How are you feeling now?

573
00:27:37,940 --> 00:27:38,780
I'm fine.

574
00:27:38,860 --> 00:27:39,860
Moving around easily.

575
00:27:39,980 --> 00:27:42,300
Why insist on coming back
from the hospital?

576
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:45,740
I just thought I could help out.

577
00:27:45,980 --> 00:27:47,420
Now that you're back,

578
00:27:48,180 --> 00:27:50,100
spend the next couple of days
playing chess with Uncle.

579
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:50,860
Fine.

580
00:27:51,260 --> 00:27:52,300
You agreed, but I won't.

581
00:27:52,660 --> 00:27:53,540
Every time I play with him,

582
00:27:53,980 --> 00:27:55,300
I end up with my general in my pocket.

583
00:27:56,460 --> 00:27:58,140
Even Uncle doesn't like
playing with you.

584
00:27:59,060 --> 00:28:00,460
Where's my sister?

585
00:28:00,660 --> 00:28:01,380
Your sister

586
00:28:01,980 --> 00:28:03,380
is something else.

587
00:28:03,460 --> 00:28:05,180
I thought if she took care of me
for a few more days,

588
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:06,500
she'd finish me off.

589
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:08,620
So I rushed back to contribute.

590
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:09,620
Okay.

591
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:12,060
It's good to be motivated.

592
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,340
I'll find something for you to do,

593
00:28:15,700 --> 00:28:17,020
so you can be comfortable

594
00:28:17,340 --> 00:28:18,620
and make contributions as well.

595
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:37,400
[Sanlianer Factory]

596
00:29:16,580 --> 00:29:17,060
Guozhu.

597
00:29:20,700 --> 00:29:21,660
Are you out of your mind?

598
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:33,520
[REC]

599
00:29:34,380 --> 00:29:35,060
Xiaoguang.

600
00:29:35,420 --> 00:29:36,300
Look at those two people over there.

601
00:29:40,860 --> 00:29:42,540
They're scavengers.

602
00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:44,300
Scavengers?

603
00:29:44,300 --> 00:29:45,900
Can you be more precise?

604
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:47,820
Strictly speaking,
that's called stealing,

605
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:49,420
not scavenging.

606
00:29:50,500 --> 00:29:52,340
And you've recorded it, haven't you?

607
00:29:55,020 --> 00:29:56,900
We've been here for ten days

608
00:29:57,540 --> 00:29:58,660
and only filmed three things.

609
00:29:58,740 --> 00:30:01,220
The scavengers

610
00:30:02,380 --> 00:30:03,540
and two drunks.

611
00:30:03,980 --> 00:30:05,740
But no deliveries.

612
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:08,980
How's your head?

613
00:30:09,020 --> 00:30:09,900
Still hurting?

614
00:30:10,820 --> 00:30:12,140
My head is fine.

615
00:30:12,220 --> 00:30:12,860
It's just...

616
00:30:15,180 --> 00:30:15,860
Your butt hurts, right?

617
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:17,020
My butt hurts too.

618
00:30:18,540 --> 00:30:20,140
Feels like it's about to fall apart.

619
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:26,620
Is that Bei?

620
00:30:27,380 --> 00:30:28,420
Do we have new leads?

621
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:30,380
It's Nan.

622
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:33,660
She sent a message to check in on me.

623
00:30:36,020 --> 00:30:37,180
Look at you,

624
00:30:37,980 --> 00:30:39,340
you can't even keep a straight face.

625
00:30:46,820 --> 00:30:47,980
Bei told us to go back.

626
00:30:48,060 --> 00:30:48,940
We're not keeping watch anymore?

627
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:51,140
The current order is for us to return.

628
00:30:51,300 --> 00:30:52,220
How can we keep watching?

629
00:31:07,860 --> 00:31:09,700
What's up with you two?

630
00:31:09,740 --> 00:31:10,660
Why the long faces?

631
00:31:12,260 --> 00:31:13,100
Where's Bei?

632
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:16,740
Bei's getting scolded right now.

633
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:18,820
Why?

634
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:20,940
The lead went cold.

635
00:31:21,420 --> 00:31:22,740
Which lead?

636
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:23,820
Sanlianer Factory.

637
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:26,380
Weren't Zhu and I just keeping watch?

638
00:31:26,420 --> 00:31:28,180
So why call us back so early?

639
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:29,620
What if we catch something today?

640
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:31,940
Let's go, Zhu. Let's go back
and continue watching.

641
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:33,420
We can't afford to miss anything.

642
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:35,300
Stop right there.

643
00:31:35,740 --> 00:31:36,460
Come back!

644
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:40,020
Bro.

645
00:32:12,820 --> 00:32:15,220
Let us go back and continue watching.

646
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:16,460
We can't lose this lead.

647
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:17,900
I promise I'll keep a close eye on it.

648
00:32:21,180 --> 00:32:22,180
It's been ten days.

649
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:27,340
The drugs on the market
haven't decreased at all.

650
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:31,060
Sanlianer Factory hasn't
made a single delivery.

651
00:32:32,620 --> 00:32:33,820
What does that tell us?

652
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:36,860
Did you guys miss something?

653
00:32:41,540 --> 00:32:44,460
We've been undercover
in several places these past few days,

654
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:48,740
and the drugs are still circulating.

655
00:32:49,860 --> 00:32:51,180
What does that tell us?

656
00:32:52,060 --> 00:32:53,900
It tells us we've been watching
the wrong place.

657
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:57,000
To be precise, the location has changed.

658
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:01,400
What about Mouse?

659
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:02,760
Has he said anything?

660
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,720
It's possible that Qin Yi was used

661
00:33:08,840 --> 00:33:10,920
to changing the storage location
periodically,

662
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:13,800
or maybe our previous surveillance

663
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:14,800
was noticed.

664
00:33:16,320 --> 00:33:17,480
But whatever the reason,

665
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,440
Sanlianer Factory

666
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:20,440
is no longer

667
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,680
the drug warehouse.

668
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:53,320
♪Memories fade, hidden in snow♪

669
00:33:56,880 --> 00:34:02,280
♪Unclear paths, where do they go?♪

670
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:12,520
♪Voices speak, nothing to show♪

671
00:34:15,240 --> 00:34:20,560
♪I can't hear my heart's flow♪

672
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:32,120
♪Time chases, past and future blend♪

673
00:34:32,720 --> 00:34:37,720
♪Ambition and doubt contend♪

674
00:34:37,720 --> 00:34:42,240
♪Facing the game♪

675
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:50,440
♪Truth hides, waiting to mend♪

676
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:55,960
♪Who sheds their blood with such pain?♪

677
00:34:55,960 --> 00:35:03,520
♪Who writes a story
of endless ruins in vain?♪

678
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:27,000
♪Truth hides, waiting to mend♪

679
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:32,520
♪Whose blood and sweat♪

680
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:40,080
♪Is painting the vivid pictures
in this tale?♪
